transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan, Mam se baat kariye aap.
Executive: Haanji, haanji.
Customer: Haan, mein bhi woh lunch pe tha aur aapka call aaya tha, abhi mein free ho gaya hu, toh aap bolna toh abhi connect kar lete.
Executive: Haan, haan, mein aa gayi bas mein, mera bhi lunch ho raha tha, shayad aapne call kari thi na? Toh.
Customer: Haan, mein mein aapko call back kiya tha. Aap toh abhi connect kar lete, 5 minute mein mein aapko message karta hu.
Executive: Aap mujhe WhatsApp pe message kar dena, mein aapko link bhej dungi, theek hai?
Customer: Haan, haan, theek hai, theek hai, okay madam, okay.
Executive: Theek hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer wants to connect with the executive.



Resolution:

- Executive asked the customer to message on WhatsApp.

- Executive will send the link to connect.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

- Neutral -> Neutral
